&#x2713;	[Sign into the Epic Games Launcher](#Bookmark3)  
&#x2713;	[Install Unreal Engine](#Bookmark4)  
&#x2713;	[Launch Unreal Engine](#Bookmark5)

Now, you're ready to start using Unreal Engine.

